00:16:23,900 --> 00:16:25,225
Scott: They live on that shtick.

275
00:16:25,346 --> 00:16:29,100
Scott: Anyway, if Jack Thompson became one of those guys, that would be a lot funnier.

276
00:16:29,540 --> 00:16:30,904
Rym: I just can't believe he's back in the news.

